                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Beaupré</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>, via consulate at Colon.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">United States Legation to Colombia</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-08-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 5, 1903</hi>.</date>
                        <lb/>(From Colon, August 18, 1903.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>No cable received since (the) 13th July, the company having closed Buenaventura
                    office. Government does not allow cables to pass over land lines. Situation
                    critical. American minister Bogota. August 5.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Malmros.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
